# Time Sphere Project Structure

This is a front-end e-commerce project built with Gulp and deployed to GitHub Pages.

## Main Entry Points
- Main build configuration: [gulpfile.js](mdc:gulpfile.js)
- Package configuration: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- Build paths configuration: [gulp/config/paths.js](mdc:gulp/config/paths.js)

## Directory Structure
- `src/` - Source files for development
  - `src/pages/` - HTML page templates
  - `src/components/` - Reusable HTML components
  - `src/styles/` - SCSS/Sass stylesheets
  - `src/js/` - JavaScript files
  - `src/img/` - Source images
  - `src/assets/` - Static assets (fonts, favicon, etc.)
- `build/` - Production build output (auto-generated)
- `docs/` - Project documentation
- `.github/workflows/` - GitHub Actions workflows

## Key Files
- [.github/workflows/deploy.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/deploy.yml) - GitHub Pages deployment workflow
- [src/pages/index.html](mdc:src/pages/index.html) - Main homepage template
- [src/components/layout/header.html](mdc:src/components/layout/header.html) - Site header
- [src/components/layout/footer.html](mdc:src/components/layout/footer.html) - Site footer
- [src/styles/main.scss](mdc:src/styles/main.scss) - Main stylesheet entry point